  • Classes in de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor used by de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor 
    Class and Description
    AbstractAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IAccessor interface.
    AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all Array properties.
    AbstractContainerItemAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and provides default behaviour for all implementations of the IAccessor interface.
    AbstractContainerPropertyAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerPropertyAccessor interface.
    AbstractListItemAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractListItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all List like properties.
    AbstractMapItemAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractMapItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all Map like properties.
    AbstractPropertyAccessorImpl
    The abstract class AbstractPropertyAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IPropertyAccessor interface.
    DefaultValueHolder
    The class DefaultValueHolder models a holder for a default value which was declared by the Property annotation's defaultValue property.
    IAccessor
    The interface IAccessor models the root of a hierarchy of derived interfaces.
    IContainerItemAccessor
    The interface IContainerItemAccess models a generic accessor for items in a container such as an Array or a List or a Map.
    IContainerPropertyAccessor
    The interface IContainerPropertyAccessor models an accessor for all container like properties such as Arrays, Lists, and Maps.
    IPropertyAccessor
    The interface IPropertyAccessor models an accessor for accessing the annotated fields in a POJO.
    RootAccessorFactory
    The final class RootAccessorFactory models a factory for instances of the IAccessor interface that represent the root of a hierarchy of accessors for traversing and accessing the properties of instances of classes that have been annotated with the PropertyClass annotation.
